overlappable-4\" data-category=\"overlappable\" class=\"overlappable-4 content-section content-section-spacing\" data-overlap=\"true\">\r\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\r\n<div  data-type=\"row\" class=\"row spaced-cols text-center spaced-fix\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding wow bounceIn\">\r\n\r\n<span  class=\"shadow-large-black round ds-evil dse1\"></span>\r\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\">\r\n<h5  class=\"\">Severity in work</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">No matter how often the player will pass the level, we take our work seriously and do not make allowances</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding wow bounceIn\">\r\n\r\n<span  class=\"shadow-large-black round ds-evil dse2\"></span>\r\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\">\r\n<h5  class=\"\">Mindfulness</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">Twice in one place the lightning does not beat, so the player can not win using the same tactics. For this, there are bugs of the game itself!</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-xs-12 col-sm-4 col-padding wow bounceIn\">\r\n\r\n<span  class=\"shadow-large-black round ds-evil dse3\"></span>\r\n<div  data-type=\"column\" class=\"\">\r\n<h5  class=\"\">Work is not the result</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">We work for the result - the player does not have to complete the level completely. At all. No way.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div  id=\"about-1\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd;\" data-label=\"About\" data-id=\"about-1\" data-export-id=\"about-1\" data-category=\"about\" class=\"about-1 content-section content-section-spacing\">\r\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\r\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\r\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h5  class=\"\">Do not believe me?</h5>\r\n<h2  class=\"\">We worked in all parts <span  face=\"Playfair Display, sans-serif\" style=\"font-family: \'Playfair Display\', sans-serif;\"><i >Dark Souls</i></span>&nbsp;and we know how to create impairments for the player!</h2>\r\n<p  class=\"lead\">Every player who met with each of us did this at least 10 times. No one was able to get through us the first time.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-xs bottom-xs flexbox image-group-bottom-3-img space-bottom-xs center-xs\"><img  class=\"wow fadeInUp left-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cropped-ds1.jpg\"> <img  class=\"wow fadeInUp center-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cropped-ds3.jpg\" data-wow-delay=\".2s\"> <img  class=\"wow fadeInUp right-img shadow-large-black\" data-size=\"500x300\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/cropped-ds2.jpg\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div  id=\"features-3\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\" data-label=\"Features\" data-id=\"features-12-card-bordered\" data-export-id=\"features-12-card-bordered\" data-category=\"features\" class=\"features-12-card-bordered content-section content-section-spacing \">\r\n<div  class=\"gridContainer\">\r\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\r\n<div  class=\"section-title-col\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h2  class=\"\">A few words about why we are the best</h2>\r\n<p  class=\"lead\">AI in modern games is designed either for a simple passage called \"story\", or \"hardcore\", when the player rolls npc in huge numbers and with a full supply of HP</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"row spaced-cols\" data-type=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div  class=\"card row-card bordered y-move wow fadeInLeft\">\r\n<div  class=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-connectdevelop round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h5  class=\"color2\">Your head</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">Each of us has his own intellect, which means that what came up in battle with one of us - does not fit with others</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div  class=\"card row-card bordered y-move wow fadeInRight\">\r\n<div  class=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon fa-codepen round bordered color2\"> </i></div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h5  class=\"color2\">Flexibility</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">We adjust to each player. So it\'s easier to anger him, to make him angry and not let him pass on.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div  class=\"card row-card bordered y-move wow fadeInLeft\" data-wow-delay=\".6s\">\r\n<div  class=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-american-sign-language-interpreting bordered round\"> </i></div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h5  class=\"color2\">Enormous HP Strip and Damage</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">At the time of the meeting with the player we always have a full band of health and a huge level of damage, we are Bosses</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-6\">\r\n<div  class=\"card row-card bordered y-move wow fadeInRight\" data-wow-delay=\".6s\">\r\n<div  class=\"row\">\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm-fit icon-column\"><i  class=\"fa icon color2 fa-bomb bordered round\"> </i></div>\r\n<div  class=\"col-sm\" data-type=\"column\">\r\n<h5  class=\"color2\">No Promises</h5>\r\n<p  class=\"\">We never go to meet the player. Even if he asks. And if he tries to pass by ... he does not pass by.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div  id=\"portfolio-3\" style=\"background-color: #f5fafd !important;\" data-label=\"Portfolio\" data-id=\"portfolio-4\" data-export-id=\"portfolio-4\" data-category=\"portfolio\" class=\"portfolio-4 content-section content-section-spacing-top\">\r\n<div  class=\"\">\r\n<div  class=\"row text-center\">\r\n<div  class=\"section-title-col