orld consisted of fog and gray rocks, among which were the trunks of stone trees. Only these immortal dragons inhabited these lands.\r\nBut deep beneath the roots of the eternal trees, fire arose and awakened creatures that found in the tongues of flame three great souls. And then they emerged from the darkness. Nito, the first of the dead. Witch Isalita and her daughter of chaos. Gwyn, the lord of light, and his faithful knights.\r\nBut there was also one more - quickly forgotten cunning dwarf, who found a special, dark, soul in the fire.\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">The birth of a new era</h3>\r\nBut soon the flame will go out, and only darkness will remain.\r\n\r\nGwynn, Nito and the witch Izalita came to the surface and challenged the dragons, believing that the acquired souls of the overlords gave them enough power to take the world to themselves. However, they had no chances in the war with the immortal and invulnerable rulers of the world. Many of the knights of Gwyn fell, not one step closer to victory.\r\n\r\nAnd then came the Nagy Sith. Being a dragon, Sith was born without stone scales, which gave his brethren immortality. Out of envy, he betrayed his family and told Gwin that the scales of his congeners are vulnerable to lightning and conceals a mortal body beneath him.\r\n\r\nThen Gwyn and his knights created a special miracle capable of summoning lightning spears. With their help they smashed the scales of the ancient dragons, Nito sent illnesses and decay to their flesh, and the witch Izalita with her daughters created fiery spouts, destroyed ancient trees and scorched rocks.\r\n\r\nSoon the dragons were defeated. Thus began the era of fire.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-143 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bdae26c86dfc81f2-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"276\" />\r\n\r\nAs fire shaped the first rulers of a new era, so they, having obtained the divine status, began to change the world around them. Among the gray rocks came life, and in the once deserted lands, cities and kingdoms began to emerge. And in the heart of the world proudly ascended the peaks of the city of gods Anor Londo, which became the capital of the kingdom of Lordran.\r\n\r\nBut life is impossible without fire. In its new guise, the world will exist only as long as the very first flame, spread throughout the world by fire, burns. For the time being, no one was worried about this.\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-144 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/96cb23ede9d51963-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"244\" />\r\n\r\nGwin after the war married an unknown girl and got three children. One is the unnamed god of war, devoid of divine status and erased from history for an alliance with the surviving original dragons. The second is Guinevere, beloved and revered by all the princess of light. And the third child is Gvindolin, the son of Gwyn, born with the power of the Moon, allowing him to create illusions.\r\n\r\nSuch abilities were traditionally attributed to women, and therefore Gvindolina was raised as a daughter. Nevertheless, he became the head of the powerful and revered covenant \"Blades of the Dark Moon,\" whose members hunted sinners. It is rumored that Gwin was also the fourth child - the daughter of Yorkshka, who received her name from Gvindolin and eventually replaced him as head of the \"blades\".','Analyze the plot of Dark Souls: the era of fire','','publish','open','open','','analyze-the-plot-of-dark-souls-the-era-of-fire','','','2018-04-22 01:53:41','2018-04-21 22:53:41','',0,'http://localhost:8000/?p=183',0,'post','',0),(184,1,'2018-04-22 01:53:41','2018-04-21 22:53:41','\"I have in my head a perfectly composed storyline of the whole series, but I\'m not going to impose it on the players. I oblige them to accept only those plot elements that are in the game itself, and on their basis they will have to build their own interpretations. Wh