d told Gwin that the scales of his congeners are vulnerable to lightning and conceals a mortal body beneath him.\r\n\r\nThen Gwyn and his knights created a special miracle capable of summoning lightning spears. With their help they smashed the scales of the ancient dragons, Nito sent illnesses and decay to their flesh, and the witch Izalita with her daughters created fiery spouts, destroyed ancient trees and scorched rocks.\r\n\r\nSoon the dragons were defeated. Thus began the era of fire.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"wp-image-143 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/bdae26c86dfc81f2-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"490\" height=\"276\" />\r\n\r\nAs fire shaped the first rulers of a new era, so they, having obtained the divine status, began to change the world around them. Among the gray rocks came life, and in the once deserted lands, cities and kingdoms began to emerge. And in the heart of the world proudly ascended the peaks of the city of gods Anor Londo, which became the capital of the kingdom of Lordran.\r\n\r\nBut life is impossible without fire. In its new guise, the world will exist only as long as the very first flame, spread throughout the world by fire, burns. For the time being, no one was worried about this.\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-144 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/96cb23ede9d51963-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"433\" height=\"244\" />\r\n\r\nGwin after the war married an unknown girl and got three children. One is the unnamed god of war, devoid of divine status and erased from history for an alliance with the surviving original dragons. The second is Guinevere, beloved and revered by all the princess of light. And the third child is Gvindolin, the son of Gwyn, born with the power of the Moon, allowing him to create illusions.\r\n\r\nSuch abilities were traditionally attributed to women, and therefore Gvindolina was raised as a daughter. Nevertheless, he became the head of the powerful and revered covenant \"Blades of the Dark Moon,\" whose members hunted sinners. It is rumored that Gwin was also the fourth child - the daughter of Yorkshka, who received her name from Gvindolin and eventually replaced him as head of the \"blades\".','Analyze the plot of Dark Souls: the era of fire','','inherit','closed','closed','','183-revision-v1','','','2018-04-22 01:53:41','2018-04-21 22:53:41','',183,'http://localhost:8000/183-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(185,1,'2018-04-22 01:57:49','2018-04-21 22:57:49','<img class=\" wp-image-147 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/207f5373fbb6b37d-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"392\" height=\"221\" />\r\n\r\nNaked Sith was rewarded with the title of Duke and a part of Gwyn\'s powerful soul. His destiny is located near Anor Londo, and there Sith founded a huge library, known as the \"archives of the Duke\". It was in them that the first knowledge of magic and crystal charms was recorded.\r\n\r\nIn the same place, Sith\'s inhuman experiments on living beings began - he dreamed of finding the secret of immortality. The Sith-minded mediums wandered the world searching for victims, but due to past merits, everything got away with it. Over time, Sith turned into a recluse and, according to rumors, he became insane. But it was not possible to check it out to anyone - the guardian he exposed did not allow anyone to access the archives.\r\n<h1>Liberation of the abyss</h1>\r\nYou\'re a strong person. Of course, your kind is much more than pure darkness. The spread of the abyss must be stopped.\r\n\r\nIn the end, the original flame began to fade away: a natural and irreversible process, foreshadowing the coming of the era of darkness and the end of Gwyn\'s power. At the same time, fires scattered all over the world began to fade away. Then Gwin found fuel for them - humanity. This mysterious substance, inherent in every person, can support the fire for a short time. But where did humanity come from, and what is it?\r\n\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-148 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/df1a17de37c0db7c-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"362\" height=\"204\" />\r\n\r\nWhile Gwyn and the other gods used great souls to achieve power and change the world, the cunning dwarf, later named Manus and possessed of a dark soul, lurked from everyone. He became the first person, and all his descendants received a piece of that darkest soul - humanity. Perhaps, the dark soul was originally the fuel of the original flame? Or did the dwarf outwit all, and each humanity burned in the fire actually only brought the darkness on?\r\n\r\nBut humanity was not the only legacy of Manus. Over time, the curse spread throughout the world: some people displayed a sign of darkness on their bodies, turning them into immortal undead. Dying, the damned reborn at the fires, losing a piece of humanity, gradually going mad and turning into \"hollow\".\r\n\r\nSociety preferred to exile them to the shelter of the undead, where they had to languish for the rest of the days. For a long time, Gwyn did not even take the threat seriously.\r\n\r\nUntil Kaas was first seen in the village of Olachil.\r\n\r\nKaas cunningly convinced the inhabitants of Olachil to open the grave of the first man. Having done this, they released not only the father of all people, but also the abyss, the inexorable enemy of all life. No one knows for sure what an abyss is. But, most likely, this is the growing and growing dark soul, once found a cunning dwarf. It is possible that the gods themselves nourished its power, feeding human humanity to the tongues of flame.\r\n\r\nThe influence of Manus perverted the humanity of the inhabitants of Olachil, turning them into horrible monsters. To prevent a catastrophe, Gwyn sent Sir Arthorias, one of the four most trusted knights, to the village. Artorias became the only one who could penetrate the struck by the abyss of the Olachil, for which he was nicknamed the \"wanderer of the abyss\". However, good luck in the campaign he did not accompany - Artorias not only failed to stop Manus, but he himself was corrupted by the abyss.\r\n\r\nBut the hour of this world has not yet come - Manus himself ruined himself. Pursuing only his goals, he tightened the chosen dead man, the damned undead from a distant future, and fell from his sword, which gave rise to the legend of Sir Artorias, who stopped the abyss.\r\n\r\nAnd the abyss was really stopped for a while, but the beginning was made, and Kaas remained alive.','Analysis of the plot, part 2','','publish','open','open','','analysis-of-the-plot-part-2','','','2018-04-22 01:57:49','2018-04-21 22:57:49','',0,'http://localhost:8000/?p=185',0,'post','',0),(186,1,'2018-04-22 01:57:49','2018-04-21 22:57:49','<img class=\" wp-image-147 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/207f5373fbb6b37d-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"392\" height=\"221\" />\r\n\r\nNaked Sith was rewarded with the title of Duke and a part of Gwyn\'s powerful soul. His destiny is located near Anor Londo, and there Sith founded a huge library, known as the \"archives of the Duke\". It was in them that the first knowledge of magic and crystal charms was recorded.\r\n\r\nIn the same place, Sith\'s inhuman experiments on living beings began - he dreamed of finding the secret of immortality. The Sith-minded mediums wandered the world searching for victims, but due to past merits, everything got away with it. Over time, Sith turned into a recluse and, according to rumors, he became insane. But it was not possible to check it out to anyone - the guardian he exposed did not allow anyone to access the archives.\r\n<h1>Liberation of the abyss</h1>\r\nYou\'re a strong person. Of course, your kind is much more than pure darkness. The spread of the abyss must be stopped.\r\n\r\nIn the end, the original flame began to fade away: a natural and irreversible process, foreshadowing the coming of the 