d them in such quantity that he grew to an incredible size and softened, after which he was locked in a temple of depths.\r\n\r\nThe origin and predilections of Aldrick make many think that under his guise lies the executioner Smog, the legendary warrior who was almost not included in the number of the knights of Gwyn. To stand on a par with Sir Arthorias, Ornstein, Siaran and Goch, he was not allowed just cannibalism - Smoog loved to crush the victims\' bones with a huge hammer and eat the remains.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/a711853cdf8ff22d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► It is said that Smoug was killed chosen a dead man many centuries ago and Aldrick them to be can not. In any case, he could easily swallow the remains of Smoog.\r\nBut the more eating Aldrick, the louder, so feed it did not stop, and the path along which people were carrying him to be eaten, was named by the victims. Many willy-nilly walked along it to perish in the womb of an insatiable cleric. There are rumors that only Horatius and Henri managed to avoid this. They must still wander these lands in search of revenge.\r\n\r\nIn the end, Aldrik became strong enough, and he was made the master of the ashes. Hardly had he wanted this, but this is not the end of his story. Aldrik reflected on the fading flame, and he had a vision of a new era - the era of the deep sea. Then he began to devour the gods.\r\n\r\nIn the acquisition of divine power, Aldrick had a powerful ally-the pontiff Salivan. About his background, almost nothing is known, but in Iritilla he achieved such influence that he became almost the king of the whole valley. Given the vision Aldrick, it is curious that some of his soldiers to the Pope handed over special rings with a dark eye. Looking into these eyes, the soldiers raged and eventually turned into animals.\r\n\r\nBy the will of the pontiff concl