ir opened a black flame and created a forbidden pyromancy based on it.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/e87b846238a5ea49.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>In his fall, Volnir became an even more terrifying creature than the Abyssal Father himself.\r\nHistory does not know for sure how his skull was in the catacombs. Perhaps, the former subjects preferred to hide the remains of the dark master overlooking the native lands. Or maybe the legionaries themselves brought the skull into the catacombs to protect the world from its corrupting influence. But they did not manage. Like the progenitor of their legion - Artorias. The abyss can not be destroyed.</div>\r\n</div>','The Epoch of Mankind, P 2','','publish','open','open','','the-epoch-of-mankind-part-2','','','2018-04-22 11:49:18','2018-04-22 08:49:18','',0,'http://localhost:8000/?p=197',0,'post','',0),(198,1,'2018-04-22 02:18:44','2018-04-21 23:18:44','<h1>Deep sea</h1>\r\nHe was made the ruler of the ashes. Not for dignity, but because of strength. Such, you see, is the master. Do we even have a chance?\r\n\r\nAldrick was born in Iritilla, a city in a cold, moonlit valley, today surrounding the once great city of the gods Anor Londo. Later Aldrik became a cleric, which, however, did not prompt him to abandon the main predilection - eating people. He devoured them in such quantity that he grew to an incredible size and softened, after which he was locked in a temple of depths.\r\n\r\nThe origin and predilections of Aldrick make many think that under his guise lies the executioner Smog, the legendary warrior who was almost not included in the number of the knights of Gwyn. To stand on a par with Sir Arthorias, Ornstein, Siaran and Goch, he was not allowed just cannibalism - Smoog loved to crush the victims\' bones with a huge hammer and eat the remains.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg