er overlooking the native lands. Or maybe the legionaries themselves brought the skull into the catacombs to protect the world from its corrupting influence. But they did not manage. Like the progenitor of their legion - Artorias. The abyss can not be destroyed.</div>\r\n</div>','The Epoch of Mankind, part 2','','inherit','closed','closed','','197-revision-v1','','','2018-04-22 02:18:44','2018-04-21 23:18:44','',197,'http://localhost:8000/197-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(199,1,'2018-04-22 02:22:38','2018-04-21 23:22:38','<div id=\"contppas\" class=\"page_article noselect\">\r\n<div class=\"page_article_content haveselect\">\r\n<div id=\"contppa\" class=\"universal_content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"old_article_content\">\r\n<h1>The King without the Kingdom</h1>\r\nMay the sun shine upon this master of ashes.\r\n\r\nGormon Jorm, the ruler of the Corrupted Capital, did not cope with his burden. Jorm fearlessly led the army into battle, personally fighting in the forefront. Thanks to a huge shield, he became invulnerable on the battlefield. But one day he could not protect and lost someone who was dear to him. Then he abandoned the shield, built himself a machete of incredible size and became even more violent in battle.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/225605fe620e62bb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The great destiny of Jorma was predetermined from the beginning, because he is a direct descendant of the lord of giants, who many years ago almost destroyed the kingdom of Vendric.\r\nOver time, the lonely Jorm became the wise ruler of the Corrupted City, the home of skilful sorcerers who considered themselves the heirs of the famous Logan Big Hat. But the inhabitants of the capital suffered because of the products of the defiled flame, long ago created by the witch Isalita. Jorm decided to sacrifice himself and become the lord of the ashes to once and for all destroy the defiled flame.\r\n\r\nJorme guessed that the process of igniting a fire could be detrimental to his reason. He decided to protect the inhabitants, handing them the sword of the Lord of Storms, the only weapon that could smash him. But there was a second such sword, and Jorm gave it to his good friend Sigvard of Catarina, taking from him the word: if something goes wrong, Sigvard must finish off the giant.\r\n\r\nPreparations were completed, and Jorm accepted his fate.\r\n\r\nHe really managed to destroy the defiled flame. Those few brave souls who have visited the ruins of the ancient Isalita say that even there the demons are almost degenerated. But the last outbreak of fire, which gave rise to chaos, took with them all the inhabitants of the Desecrated capital. Perhaps, it was then that Jorm became indifferent to the fate of the world. Awakened by the sound of the bell, he simply returned to his deserted city.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>Blue blood</h1>\r\nThe master\'s mantle does not interest me. The curse of the ignition of fire, the legacy of the rulers, but burn it all with fire. You\'ve done enough already, it\'s time for you to rest.\r\n\r\nBut there were two more: a modest man who humbly accepted his destiny, and one who refused to fulfill his destiny.\r\n\r\nLudlet Kurlyandsky, the only one of all the overlords, took the throne placed to him at the first bell of the bell. Ludlet is a man with a mysterious past, almost nothing is known about him. Like Kurland, the country from which he was expelled. But somehow these mysterious lands became famous. For example, transposition - the art of making from the contaminated souls objects that enclose their essence. In the rest of the world, such activities are strictly forbidden.\r\n\r\nOnce Ludlett was familiar with the guardian of fire, which could look into the abyss and saw there a betrayal - a dark future without fire. Then the exile decided to kindle a flame.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/1fbd9a074f9a072d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► Ludlet clearly occupies an important place in history, perhaps we will hear about it.\r\nThe second is Prince Lautric, the youngest son of Oceuros, the former king of the lands surrounding the castle of Lotrick. The mother of Lothrick was Guinevere, the princess of light and the beloved daughter of Gwyn. Nobody knows when and why she came to these lands, but here she was known as a kind and caring woman, blessing the knights, who are guarding the homeland.\r\n\r\nThe prince was born weak and painful, barely able to move independently. Nevertheless, he had an important place in the history of his native kingdom - Lotrik, like Gwyn once, was to become the master of the ashes.\r\n\r\nBut he refused.\r\n\r\nSince childhood, Lotrik was brought up by a sage who questioned the necessity of burning a flame. Perhaps it was his teaching that influenced the prince. And maybe Lotrick himself decided. The cycle of igniting a fire he called a curse, determined to calmly watch the fading flame. In the end, darkness is not only an endless night, but also an endless peace.\r\n\r\nIt\'s easy to believe that Lotrick is simply tired of life and since childhood he was disappointed in her. After all, as they say, he was born not only weak, but also disfigured. All his life he wore a deaf hooded sweatshirt, and all that could be seen was his hands with long clawed fingers. Like a dragon.\r\n\r\nA simple coincidence? His father, King Oceiros, was in the cult of Naked Sith, studying the legacy of the original dragon and the greatest explorer of his works - Logan the Great Hat. What experiments conducted the cult, it is not known, but they ended with the conversion of the king into a vile being, reminiscent of both human and dragon without scales.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/6d7297c087922d0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The body of the changed Oceiros is covered with unusual outgrowths. It\'s strange, but people speak the same formations in a different story, mentioning a certain Master Willem.\r\nLautric had an older brother, Laurian, supposedly born before the Oeceroos entered the cult. Laurian grew up as a strong young man and became a brave knight. But one day something changed in him, and he voluntarily shared the curse of his brother.\r\n\r\nAnother rumor is that he once swung his prince-demon with his sword, and the blade was saturated with the power of chaos. Since then, the sword exudes a damned flame, becoming its source. Perhaps, in it the reason for the appearance above the castle of strange flying creatures, so resembling the creatures of the bed of chaos?\r\n\r\nBe that as it may, it is certainly not for us to know, and their purpose remains unknown.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/0a271088fa4eb134.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>► The brothers divided each other\'s fates, and their souls almost merged into one.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>Dead gods</h1>\r\nThe age of fire began with the old gods, and it was supported by fire. But the gods are no more, and the omnipotent fire is worthy of a successor. Of course, such as the master of the devastated, who will try on the true mask of mankind.\r\n\r\nAt all times, however dark they may be, was the chosen dead man. And so it happened again. The fireless rose from the grave and came to the temple of fire. The last guardian directed him and helped to gain and build strength from the souls absorbed in the battle.\r\n\r\nOne by one, the ascendants of the ashes fell from his blade. Their ashes were burned, and the passage to the crucible of the first flame was opened. There, beyond time and space, surrounded by all past ages, the dead man met the Soul of Ashes, the embodiment of the souls of all those who once supported the flame. And even this immortal creature was defeated. What next?\r\n\r\nSome say that the dead man did not hesitate to ignite the flame again, but the fire was so weak that hope was scarcely glimmering among timidly dancing languages ​​- one day the flame would die definitively, and there would be nothing left. Others say that the thirst for power seized the hero and he tried to steal the flame, filling his body with his power. If so, the dead man was stupid - a simple undead can never cope with the force that even the ancient gods could not curb.\r\n\r\nBut some whisper that it was not so.\r\n\r\nThe hero on his journey came to a strange place: a cluster of abandoned graves, an all-consuming darkness and an exact replica of the fire temple in the center. But inside was empty, and only the temple servant welcomed the hero. There he found the eyes of the guardian of fire. The very ones that saw betrayal and the abyss.\r\n\r\nWhat kind of place is it? Perhaps - the temple, where once burned the flame Ludlet. But maybe the dead man looked into the future, the very place where the flame went out and the darkness covered the world. This journey made the hero think. He presented the eyes of his keeper, and she also saw the abyss and opened the entire picture before the hero. He was fascinated by the tranquility of the darkness, and the flame slowly died away.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/5cb96a3394dd4c42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► But one day the little lights will reel in the dark again. And the keeper will always be drawn to them.\r\nHowever, there is one more version. It is full of darkness and cruelty, hardly anyone will want to believe it, but in reality it was so. The dead met the pilgrim Joel from the distant lands of London, the kingdom of the \"hollow\" undead, admirers of the abyss and the homeland of the most repulsive rituals. The Pilgrim released the true power of the hero, revealing on his body marks that oozed by the darkest and purest humanity, and the non-fervent became \"hollow.\" The abyss did not possess it, but it became its integral part.\r\n\r\nThen came Yuri, one of the abbesses of the Black Church of London and a faithful servant of Kaas\' primogeniture. It is she who discovered the ignorant true destiny of the undead. The gods are dead. None of those who once found in the first flame the soul of the overlords did not remain, but their ignition ritual continues to live, interfering with the natural course of things. The era of the gods has passed, the era of darkness and the abyss - the era of people has come. The curse of the undead can not be defeated, because this is not a curse at all. To be \"hollow\" is the natural state of a person. All that is needed is \"hollow\", so it is a monarch, a dark master who will lead them into a new era.\r\n\r\nAnd the ignorant became it. He not only appropriated the flame, he absorbed it, made a part of himself. The curse is gone, the cycle is stopped forever.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/d34d0cef831c495e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','The Epoch of Mankind, P 3','','publish','open','open','','the-epoch-of-mankind-part-3','','','2018-04-22 11:48:54','2018-04-22 08:48:54','',0,'http://localhost:8000/?p=199',0,'post','',0),(200,1,'2018-04-22 02:22:38','2018-04-21 23:22:38','<div id=\"contppas\" class=\"page_article noselect\">\r\n<div class=\"page_article_content haveselect\">\r\n<div id=\"contppa\" class=\"universal_content clearfix\">\r\n<div class=\"old_article_content\">\r\n<h1>The King without the Kingdom</h1>\r\nMay the sun shine upon this master of ashes.\r\n\r\nGormon Jorm, the ruler of the Corrupted Capital, did not cope with his burden. Jorm fearlessly led the army into battle, personally fighting in the forefront. Thanks to a huge shield, he became invulnerable on the battlefield. But one day he could not protect and lost someone who was dear to him. Then he abandoned the shield, built himself a machete of incredible size and became even more violent in battle.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/225605fe620e62bb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The great destiny of Jorma was predetermined from the beginning, because he is a direct descendant of the lord of giants, who many years ago almost destroyed the kingdom of Vendric.\r\nOver time, the lonely Jorm became the wise ruler of the Corrupted City, the home of skilful sorcerers who considered themselves the heirs of the famous Logan Big Hat. But the inhabitants of the capital suffered because of the products of the defiled flame, long ago created by the witch Isalita. Jorm decided to sacrifice himself and become the lord of the ashes to once and for all destroy the defiled flame.\r\n\r\nJorme guessed that the process of igniting a fire could be detrimental to his reason. He decided to protect the inhabitants, handing them the sword of the Lord of Storms, the only weapon that could smash him. But there was a second such sword, and Jorm gave it to his good friend Sigvard of Catarina, taking from him the word: if something goes wrong, Sigvard must finish off the giant.\r\n\r\nPreparations were completed, and Jorm accepted his fate.\r\n\r\nHe really managed to destroy the defiled flame. Those few brave souls who have visited the ruins of the ancient Isalita say that even there the demons are almost degenerated. But the last outbreak of fire, which gave rise to chaos, took with them all the inhabitants of the Desecrated capital. Perhaps, it was then that Jorm became indifferent to the fate of the world. Awakened by the sound of the bell, he simply returned to his deserted city.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>Blue blood</h1>\r\nThe master\'s mantle does not interest me. The curse of the ignition of fire, the legacy of the rulers, but burn it all with fire. You\'ve done enough already, it\'s time for you to rest.\r\n\r\nBut there were two more: a modest man who humbly accepted his destiny, and one who refused to fulfill his destiny.\r\n\r\nLudlet Kurlyandsky, the only one of all the overlords, took the throne placed to him at the first bell of the bell. Ludlet is a man with a mysterious past, almost nothing is known about him. Like Kurland, the country from which he was expelled. But somehow these mysterious lands became famous. For example, transposition - the art of making from the contaminated souls objects that enclose their essence. In the rest of the world, such activities are strictly forbidden.\r\n\r\nOnce Ludlett was familiar with the guardian of fire, which could look into the abyss and saw there a betrayal - a dark future without fire. Then the exile decided to kindle a flame.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/1fbd9a074f9a072d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► Ludlet clearly occupies an important place in history, perhaps we will hear about it.\r\nThe second is Prince Lautric, the youngest son of Oceuros, the former king of the lands surrounding the castle of Lotrick. The mother of Lothrick was Guinevere, the princess of light and the beloved daughter of Gwyn. Nobody knows when and why she came to these lands, but here she was known as a kind and caring woman, blessing the knights, who are guarding the homeland.\r\n\r\nThe prince was born weak and painful, barely able to move independently. Nevertheless, he had an important place in the history of his native kingdom - Lotrik, like Gwyn once, was to become the master of the ashes.\r\n\r\nBut he refused.\r\n\r\nSince childhood, Lotrik was brought up by a sage who questioned the necessity of burning a flame. Perhaps it was his teaching that influenced the prince. And maybe Lotrick himself decided. The cycle of igniting a fire he called a curse, determined to calmly watch the fading flame. In the end, darkness is not only an endless night, but also an endless peace.\r\n\r\nIt\'s easy to believe that Lotrick is simply tired of life and since childhood he was disappointed in her. After all, as they say, he was born not only weak, but also disfigured. All his life he wore a deaf hooded sweatshirt, and all that could be seen was his hands with long clawed fingers. Like a dragon.\r\n\r\nA simple coincidence? His father, King Oceiros, was in the cult of Naked Sith, studying the legacy of the original dragon and the greatest explorer of his works - Logan the Great Hat. What experiments conducted the cult, it is not known, but they ended with the conversion of the king into a vile being, reminiscent of both human and dragon without scales.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/6d7297c087922d0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The body of the changed Oceiros is covered with unusual outgrowths. It\'s strange, but people speak the same formations in a different story, mentioning a certain Master Willem.\r\nLautric had an older brother, Laurian, supposedly born before the Oeceroos entered the cult. Laurian grew up as a strong young man and became a brave knight. But one day something changed in him, and he voluntarily shared the curse of his brother.\r\n\r\nAnother rumor is that he once swung his prince-demon with his sword, and the blade was saturated with the power of chaos. Since then, the sword exudes a damned flame, becoming its source. Perhaps, in it the reason for the appearance above the castle of strange flying creatures, so resembling the creatures of the bed of chaos?\r\n\r\nBe that as it may, it is certainly not for us to know, and their purpose remains unknown.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/0a271088fa4eb134.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>► The brothers divided each other\'s fates, and their souls almost merged into one.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>Dead gods</h1>\r\nThe age of fire began with the old gods, and it was supported by fire. But the gods are no more, and the omnipotent fire is worthy of a successor. Of course, such as the master of the devastated, who will try on the true mask of mankind.\r\n\r\nAt all times, however dark they may be, was the chosen dead man. And so it happened again. The fireless rose from the grave and came to the temple of fire. The last guardian directed him and helped to gain and build strength from the souls absorbed in the battle.\r\n\r\nOne by one, the ascendants of the ashes fell from his blade. Their ashes were burned, and the passage to the crucible of the first flame was opened. There, beyond time and space, surrounded by all past ages, the dead man met the Soul of Ashes, the embodiment of the souls of all those who once supported the flame. And even this immortal creature was defeated. What next?\r\n\r\nSome say that the dead man did not hesitate to ignite the flame again, but the fire was so weak that hope was scarcely glimmering among timidly dancing languages ​​- one day the flame would die definitively, and there would be nothing left. Others say that the thirst for power seized the hero and he tried to steal the flame, filling his body with his power. If so, the dead man was stupid - a simple undead can never cope with the force that even the ancient gods could not curb.\r\n\r\nBut some whisper that it was not so.\r\n\r\nThe hero on his journey came to a strange place: a cluster of abandoned graves, an all-consuming darkness and an exact replica of the fire temple in the center. But inside was empty, and only the temple servant welcomed the hero. There he found the eyes of the guardian of fire. The very ones that saw betrayal and the abyss.\r\n\r\nWhat kind of place is it? Perhaps - the temple, where once burned the flame Ludlet. But maybe the dead man looked into the future, the very place where the flame went out and the darkness covered the world. This journey made the hero think. He presented the eyes of his keeper, and she also saw the abyss and opened the entire picture before the hero. He was fascinated by the tranquility of the darkness, and the flame slowly died away.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/5cb96a3394dd4c42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► But one day the little lights will reel in the dark again. And the keeper will always be drawn to them.\r\nHowever, there is one more version. It is full of darkness and cruelty, hardly anyone will want to believe it, but in reality it was so. The dead met the pilgrim Joel from the distant lands of London, the kingdom of the \"hollow\" undead, admirers of the abyss and the homeland of the most repulsive rituals. The Pilgrim released the true power of the hero, revealing on his body marks that oozed by the darkest and purest humanity, and the non-fervent became \"hollow.\" The abyss did not possess it, but it became its integral part.\r\n\r\nThen came Yuri, one of the abbesses of the Black Church of London and a faithful servant of Kaas\' primogeniture. It is she who discovered the ignorant true destiny of the undead. The gods are dead. None of those who once found in the first flame the soul of the overlords did not remain, but their ignition ritual continues to live, interfering with the natural course of things. The era of the gods has passed, the era of darkness and the abyss - the era of people has come. The curse of the undead can not be defeated, because this is not a curse at all. To be \"hollow\" is the natural state of a person. All that is needed is \"hollow\", so it is a monarch, a dark master who will lead them into a new era.\r\n\r\nAnd the ignorant became it. He not only appropriated the flame, he absorbed it, made a part of himself. The curse is gone, the cycle is stopped forever.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/a/a/f/e/b/27783/html/img/d34d0cef831c495e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','The Epoch of Mankind, Part 3','','inherit','closed','closed','','199-revision-v1','','','2018-04-22 02:22:38','2018-04-21 23:22:38','',199,'http://localhost:8000/199-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(201,1,'2018-04-22 02:28:09','2018-04-21 23:28:09','You coped with the horror in Yarnama and made it so that humanity saw a new dawn. You scattered the fog-generating fog and saved the souls of Bolletarians. But, more importantly, it was you who again ignited the first flame in Lordrana, prolonging the era of fire and delaying the oncoming cold abyss.\r\n\r\nAnd you did it again - in Dranglick, the land of the damned kings.\r\n\r\nBut sooner or later everything comes to an end.\r\n\r\nWhat are you, burning, unworthy even death, will do when the abyss approaches you close and from the first flame there will be only a handful of dry ashes? Will you go to seek the overlords of the ashes who left their half-decayed thrones, as your destiny requires?\r\n\r\nBut we are the true legends, and we will have the courage to light the fire.\r\n\r\nIt is not good for us to grovel before them. You do not think so?\r\n<div class=\"video_block\"><iframe src=\"https://www.igromania.ru/video/embed/16194/\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n<h1>Ghosts of Ancient Times</h1>\r\nTraveling through the poisoned lands of Dranglick in Dark Souls 2, we constantly stumbled upon the artifacts of the era of the Lordana. Blunted swords and armor scratched in countless battles, ancient spells and magic rings with barely visible engraving ... The fallen kingdom was literally stuffed with artifacts from the distant past.\r\n\r\nHowever, by that time the world had already changed. On these very lands, many kingdoms have blossomed and fallen, leaving behind even dilapidated ruins. The names of the great heroes of Lordawn have long been obliterated from the pages of history.\r\n\r\nBut as for millennia, cities buried underground sometimes return to the sublunary world again, thanks to the efforts of the researchers, so Lordrand again shows himself to the world. Ancient tomes, long searches and inquisitive minds do their work, and in the speech of the heroes and descriptions of objects again pop up familiar names. Logan Big Hat, Naked Sith, Gwin Ash Lord and his legion of silver knights - all those without whom it is impossible to imagine the history of the first Dark Souls, is here again.\r\n\r\nAnd although their times have long since passed, they will still play their role in the history of this world.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; cursor: zoom-in;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/43293317c57f139a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The invariable symbol of the series, the sword of moonlight, will meet here too. But even he from Easter eggs turned into a link. His presence is particularly disturbing to those who are imbued with the story of The Old Hunters.\r\nPerhaps, people were drawn to the knowledge of the ancient era unconsciously, driven by despair? The fire is almost extinguished, the ringing of the bell echoes in the vicinity of the castle of Lotrik, and the thrones of the lords of the ashes are emptied. Without rulers, it is impossible to illuminate the world with the flickering of fire. And only the damned undead, unworthy of being ashes, can find them.\r\n\r\nThe plot does not rely on the foundations laid down in the previous parts. There is no cursed king who has destroyed his kingdom, the abyss does not manifest itself so clearly, and even hollows no longer play a leading role - henceforth we are constrained by another curse.\r\n\r\nThe feeling of hopelessness and despair has always been firmly associated with the series, but in Dark Souls 3 in every bit of history it is felt that this journey is the last. In such a deplorable state, we have not yet seen this world. But do not forget that the superficial study of the story in the games of the series does not suffer. It is disclosed only before the most meticulous. It is necessary to look very closely. Long, long look into the abyss. It\'s not as it seems to you.\r\n\r\nThe next chosen dead man will go the trails of heroic predecessors, but it is not so easy to discern the familiar outlines in the new lands. Time ruthlessly - impregnable fortresses long ago turned into dust, in place of majestic castles new walls have grown, once flowering gardens are drowning in poisonous slime, and where the sun once shone, ruthless cold rules. Today these lands and kingdoms are called quite differently, but we will remember their true names. Or is it just an illusion? Evil joke of the abyss, for centuries trying to absorb the world? In Dark Souls you need to look in all eyes, but, as before, do not believe blindly everything that you see.\r\n\r\nAnd not every traveler, this world will reveal its secrets. In place of tiny dungeons and cozy glades from the second part came large mazes and marshes, where it\'s easy to get lost, - its own \"defiled valley\" is sure to be found. And to find all the hiding places and hidden paths, you\'ll have to rummage through every corner and knock with a sword on every suspicious stone - just like in the first Dark Souls. For a not-too-lucky pilgrim, travel in general can be half as long. It only remains to rely on your attentiveness and the hints of travelers from other worlds.\r\n\r\nBut I do not have to puzzle over the question of \"where to go and what to do\". Goals are perfectly read, and the road is just one. True, for the time being. At first the game helps to avoid unpleasant encounters with horrors, which the hero still has the teeth, but as soon as he accumulates enough souls, the world will release his cold hand, and after that the paths and goals will have to be found independently. Careless travelers run the risk of getting stuck and getting lost ...\r\n\r\n... but you did know what you subscribed to?\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"artimage_block\"><a><img class=\"artimg\" title=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/3412140be013b120.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<table class=\"mit_table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; width: 318px;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/ec480cfe380f0816.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td><img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; width: 318px;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/e10994b63e93fde4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mit_desc\" colspan=\"2\">►New locations adopted the severe medieval forms from the first Dark Souls, and the refined \"Victorian\" curves of the Bloodborne. But the main thing is that they still can tell the whole story without words, with their own appearance.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nBut the game fully rewards for the time spent. At the most persistent researchers all the fragments of the mosaic will form a single picture, the sequence of events will be restored, and the whole series will merge into one big story. But for this you have to cling literally for each thread, study every bit of information and read a lot between the lines. The series has remained true to the principles of plot submission, so nobody will speak to you directly.\r\n<h1>Conquering the North</h1>\r\nBut the lands on which our chosen dead man wanders, the world of Dark Souls 3 is not limited. Around there are many kingdoms and principalities, and most of them we have heard more than once. The call of the ashes spreads everywhere. The devastated pilgrims from London, the noble knights of Mirra and Astor, the wise wizards of Vinheim - all draw together to the castle of Lotrik, trying to find the missing lords. Or pursuing your own goals.\r\n\r\nMany of them will meet you on the road and become reliable allies or bitter enemies. Sometimes it depends on your actions, and sometimes - just a blind fate, but, anyway, random acquaintances here are not trusted to be trusted. And let the story lines connected with the opposing heroes, in comparison with the first part, be diminished, each of them takes for the soul no worse than the journey of the good-natured Knight Soler, and the denouement of some stories may seem cruel even by the standards of the Dark Souls series.\r\n<div class=\"artimage_block\"><a><img class=\"artimg\" title=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/3b33a111f807ecf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<table class=\"mit_table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/7995c10d6513ab79.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/dc99a57a1288cec5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mit_desc\" colspan=\"2\">► All without exception, the characters in Dark Souls 3 are important. Everyone can more deeply reveal the story and bring the player closer to understanding what is happening, and some, under certain circumstances, can seriously affect the course of global history. Keep your eyes open!</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nTraditionally, many characters do not sit with sydnam, so familiar faces come across the whole game in the most unexpected places. They will brighten up the way with a conversation, help you cope with the next boss, leaving your sign of appeal, or try to cut your throat.\r\n\r\nBut the craving for changing places is not inherent in everyone. Some prefer the warm and safe roof of the fire temple - our new Majula. With a kind of temple painfully reminiscent of the Nexus from Demon\'s Souls, even the layout is almost the same. All the merchants here will come up here, you will improve weapons from old friend André, and here the guardian of fire will increase the strength of the chosen dead in exchange for the souls absorbed in the battle. Long bustle between traders from the first Dark Souls has remained in the past, which can not but rejoice.\r\n\r\nInitially, the merchants very modest, even ascetic range: fire bombs, simple spells and a couple of embers that have replaced humanities and human figures. It only works for your first outings. Of course, they are ready to offer and much more entertaining goods, but first you have to sweat. So, the maid at the temple will ask for special ash, and the pyromancers and magicians will require folio and ancient scriptures, according to which they will be able to teach the hero new knowledge.\r\n\r\nOn the road, all this is not lying around, so for the best equipment and the most powerful spells you will have to treble each level with tripled attention. Dark Souls used to evoke the desire to collect all-all, not even the most useful things, now this \"kleptomania\" is fueled by the desire to \"pump out\" its merchants to the limit, and it is almost impossible to cope with this desire.\r\n\r\nOf course, all this is not necessary, but otherwise you not only significantly complicate your already difficult game, but also lose a huge layer of history: the items in Dark Souls 3 are still the best of the storytellers.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/bffc2f6601693bf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>► The old thief Serokrys can get new equipment, doing his craft. But that\'s where he goes to steal and what happens to those whose things he gladly sells to you, a scoundrel does not admit anything.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1>The nightmare returns</h1>\r\nDue to a more flexible set of starting classes, any equipment from the very beginning benefits. In addition to traditional warriors, knights and clerics, hybrids also appeared. For example, a killer who uses light weapons and already knows the combat spell at the start, or a herald who can not only deftly swing a spear, but also heal himself with magic.\r\n\r\nFighters, within a single battle divide the air with twin blades, covered with a shield and watering enemies with mystic fire, is not uncommon at all. It\'s not easy to play such \"masters of all trades\", but it\'s fascinating - all the mechanics are in the palm of your hand.\r\n\r\nHowever, the usual types in combat are felt differently - the experience of Bloodborne was not in vain. Enemies are constantly attacking groups and attacking with a whole series of swift strikes - from this even the strongest shield will not save. From now on even supporters of the defensive style will have to learn the ruts and parry.\r\n\r\nYour hero, however, also waving arms much faster than before, and after a couple of hours of training to find a window for the attack is not so difficult. The shield is more suitable for repelling those blows, which are too late to jump off.\r\n\r\nLimitations the game does not impose - long and stubbornly developing the character with emphasis on strength and physical strength, you can get an impenetrable \"tank\" that hides behind the shield for a long time, repulsing all attacks, and then completes the matter with one powerful swing.\r\n\r\nBut now this is not the easiest way.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/50ac9deac12423eb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► Covenants have not disappeared. True, there are essentially no new ones among them, and almost all of them are somehow connected with PvP.\r\nThe most significant changes have touched the fans to water enemies with magic, fire and miracles. The band of mana (concentration) returned, and henceforth it will not be possible to charge the counter of using the spell with five identical powerful scrolls, like a machine gun: how much your stock is enough, shoot so many times. This approach smoothes out the balance - weak initial-level spells concentrate very carefully, and even the beginning magician no longer has to swing the sword instead of the staff in order to save. But the most destructive spell even an experienced sorcerer can use only a few times, so that it will not be possible to drown the enemy in the spears of the soul.\r\n\r\nBut do not think that concentration is important only for magicians, - warriors without it, too, can not do. Each weapon now has a fighting stance, replacing the standard attacks with more powerful attacks. Crushing blows on the area, fire and magic damage, complicated feints and jumps - there are lots of options, and everyone can use it.\r\n\r\nBut the concentration of such a fighting style absorbs incredibly fast. It can be restored only with the aid of a jar with blue aestus. The catch is that you have only one set of flasks, and you have to decide how much to allocate for the therapeutic estus, and how much for the restoring concentration. The choice is really complicated: the first pieces, with whose help it is possible to increase the reserves of estus, will begin to come across very soon.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/0141a5e3200fc033.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► At first the jars are restored to ridiculously little health and concentration, and the special bones that should be burned in the fire temple to increase the effectiveness of the estus are well hidden.\r\nUnder the new style of battles, the game world was also adjusted. Inhabitants of the neighborhood of Lothrick monsters are much more insidious than most monsters from the first and second Dark Souls. The influence of the nightmares of Yarnama is felt here, just like cursed beasts, opponents are often transformed, growing tentacles and devils knows what else, or changing racks on the move, completely rearranging the style of attack.\r\n\r\nIn this case, they often walk in small groups, and in such \"flying squads\" there can easily be several types of enemies. Here, willy-nilly will have to make full use of the potential of the weapon, otherwise the estus and the nearest fire will not suffice.\r\n\r\nHowever, this is just a preparation for a meeting with the bosses. At the Japanese forums there are complaints that some of them alone can not be killed. This, of course, is not so, but many are really more complicated than before.\r\n\r\nIn Dark Souls, 3 bosses are much faster and more aggressive, and almost every strike deals with the frequency and speed of Gwyn, while, like ordinary opponents, regularly changing sets of attacks. But for everyone there is a key - reduced resistance to certain types of damage, vulnerable points, the ability to parry some attacks - it only needs to be found. True, closer to the middle of the battle, most bosses tend to radically change their behavior and turn into almost new enemies, but this is also Dark Souls, what else did you expect?\r\n\r\n<a><img class=\"artimg\" title=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/d44b5406a59c57ff.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<table class=\"mit_table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/81f54e082fbe5156.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/3842c593f616a9d7.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mit_desc\" colspan=\"2\">► In the design of bosses and rank-and-file opponents, just like Bloodborne, Lovecraft\'s influence is felt. Particularly attentive will make out even some familiar outlines. And this, believe me, not for nothing.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<div class=\"a_old_spoilerhide_block\">\r\n<div class=\"a_old_spoilerhide_1\">\r\n\r\nIn a few words about multiplayer and covens\r\nPeople play in Souls for years, not only through the full secrets of the world, but also the online component. Dark phantoms - other players suddenly invading your world and finishing you off after a skirmish with a group of especially dangerous opponents - is almost a symbol of the series. And the group hunt for bosses in the re-passage, when all the opponents are twice brutalized, is an indispensable entertainment.\r\n\r\nPreviously, such a leisure provided a system of covenants, a local analogue of guilds, but in Bloodborne this component was severely curtailed. The covenants were only three, and they were hidden so that they showed up only a couple of months after the release. Fortunately, in this aspect, Dark Souls 3 refers to the experience of the first and second parts: there are many \"guilds\" here, and finding most of them is not so difficult.\r\n\r\nFurther - moderate power spoilers. Caution.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"a_old_spoilerhide_3\">\r\n<div class=\"a_old_spoilerhide_5\">\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg_notext\"><a><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/7e06125f6a560200.jpg\" width=\"570\" height=\"321\" /></a></div>\r\nThe covenants themselves have not changed much, and some of them have migrated from the past. There are \"Warriors of the Sun\", helping each other deal with difficult bosses, and \"Azure Way\" with \"Blue Guardians\", which repel invaders. Now, however, they were joined by the \"Blades of the Dark Moon\", formerly hunted by sinners.\r\n\r\nAdherents of the ways of meanness and cunning also have a choice. Thus, the members of the Rosary Fingers invade other worlds - to snatch more enemy tongues to offer to the silent goddess, and mad marauders cut their throats even to those who call them to help. If you miss the forest hunters, then \"Farron Watch Dogs\" and \"Faithful Aldrika\" are at your service - both covenants specialize in punishing the careless travelers who have wandered into forbidden territories.\r\n\r\nHow to study the system of covenants before the release failed - too few people are playing online, but judging by what they saw and the experience of the previous parts, problems should not arise. Is that technical, but we\'ll keep you posted.\r\n\r\n* * *\r\nDark Souls 3 absorbed everything from everywhere, including the already-forgotten Demon\'s Souls and the recent Bloodborne. The game has become more modern and more convenient: here, for example, as in the second part, from the very beginning you can freely teleport between bonfires and, as in Bloodborne, it is allowed right in inventory to change the covenants found at any moment. Did the game become easier? Do not bring the gods!\r\n\r\nDark Souls 3, perhaps - the most difficult part of the series. But its complexity is not expressed by the need to nag through the whole map for an hour to improve the sword by one more level. No.\r\n\r\nHere you need to carefully look for an approach to each opponent and boss, learn to change tactics on the move and use all available means in battle; finally, it is just necessary to carefully study the levels.\r\n\r\nAnd this, perhaps, is the ideal embodiment of the philosophy of the whole series.\r\n\r\nBut, more importantly, for seven years the series did not die out. Each new part picked up the ideas of the previous one, supplemented them with new ones and presented them in such a way as to be felt in a new way. During the passage of Dark Souls 3 and thought does not arise that you play the same game for seven years. Even in spite of the four passed parts of the series behind the shoulders.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','The decayed soul. Review of Dark Souls 3','','publish','open','open','','the-decayed-soul-review-of-dark-souls-3','','','2018-04-22 02:28:09','2018-04-21 23:28:09','',0,'http://localhost:8000/?p=201',0,'post','',0),(202,1,'2018-04-22 02:28:09','2018-04-21 23:28:09','You coped with the horror in Yarnama and made it so that humanity saw a new dawn. You scattered the fog-generating fog and saved the souls of Bolletarians. But, more importantly, it was you who again ignited the first flame in Lordrana, prolonging the era of fire and delaying the oncoming cold abyss.\r\n\r\nAnd you did it again - in Dranglick, the land of the damned kings.\r\n\r\nBut sooner or later everything comes to an end.\r\n\r\nWhat are you, burning, unworthy even death, will do when the abyss approaches you close and from the first flame there will be only a handful of dry ashes? Will you go to seek the overlords of the ashes who left their half-decayed thrones, as your destiny requires?\r\n\r\nBut we are the true legends, and we will have the courage to light the fire.\r\n\r\nIt is not good for us to grovel before them. You do not think so?\r\n<div class=\"video_block\"><iframe src=\"https://www.igromania.ru/video/embed/16194/\" width=\"300\" height=\"150\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-mce-fragment=\"1\"></iframe></div>\r\n<h1>Ghosts of Ancient Times</h1>\r\nTraveling through the poisoned lands of Dranglick in Dark Souls 2, we constantly stumbled upon the artifacts of the era of the Lordana. Blunted swords and armor scratched in countless battles, ancient spells and magic rings with barely visible engraving ... The fallen kingdom was literally stuffed with artifacts from the distant past.\r\n\r\nHowever, by that time the world had already changed. On these very lands, many kingdoms have blossomed and fallen, leaving behind even dilapidated ruins. The names of the great heroes of Lordawn have long been obliterated from the pages of history.\r\n\r\nBut as for millennia, cities buried underground sometimes return to the sublunary world again, thanks to the efforts of the researchers, so Lordrand again shows himself to the world. Ancient tomes, long searches and inquisitive minds do their work, and in the speech of the heroes and descriptions of objects again pop up familiar names. Logan Big Hat, Naked Sith, Gwin Ash Lord and his legion of silver knights - all those without whom it is impossible to imagine the history of the first Dark Souls, is here again.\r\n\r\nAnd although their times have long since passed, they will still play their role in the history of this world.\r\n<div class=\"awim_wideimg\">\r\n\r\n<img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; cursor: zoom-in;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/43293317c57f139a.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"647\" height=\"364\" border=\"0\" />\r\n<div>\r\n\r\n► The invariable symbol of the series, the sword of moonlight, will meet here too. But even he from Easter eggs turned into a link. His presence is particularly disturbing to those who are imbued with the story of The Old Hunters.\r\nPerhaps, people were drawn to the knowledge of the ancient era unconsciously, driven by despair? The fire is almost extinguished, the ringing of the bell echoes in the vicinity of the castle of Lotrik, and the thrones of the lords of the ashes are emptied. Without rulers, it is impossible to illuminate the world with the flickering of fire. And only the damned undead, unworthy of being ashes, can find them.\r\n\r\nThe plot does not rely on the foundations laid down in the previous parts. There is no cursed king who has destroyed his kingdom, the abyss does not manifest itself so clearly, and even hollows no longer play a leading role - henceforth we are constrained by another curse.\r\n\r\nThe feeling of hopelessness and despair has always been firmly associated with the series, but in Dark Souls 3 in every bit of history it is felt that this journey is the last. In such a deplorable state, we have not yet seen this world. But do not forget that the superficial study of the story in the games of the series does not suffer. It is disclosed only before the most meticulous. It is necessary to look very closely. Long, long look into the abyss. It\'s not as it seems to you.\r\n\r\nThe next chosen dead man will go the trails of heroic predecessors, but it is not so easy to discern the familiar outlines in the new lands. Time ruthlessly - impregnable fortresses long ago turned into dust, in place of majestic castles new walls have grown, once flowering gardens are drowning in poisonous slime, and where the sun once shone, ruthless cold rules. Today these lands and kingdoms are called quite differently, but we will remember their true names. Or is it just an illusion? Evil joke of the abyss, for centuries trying to absorb the world? In Dark Souls you need to look in all eyes, but, as before, do not believe blindly everything that you see.\r\n\r\nAnd not every traveler, this world will reveal its secrets. In place of tiny dungeons and cozy glades from the second part came large mazes and marshes, where it\'s easy to get lost, - its own \"defiled valley\" is sure to be found. And to find all the hiding places and hidden paths, you\'ll have to rummage through every corner and knock with a sword on every suspicious stone - just like in the first Dark Souls. For a not-too-lucky pilgrim, travel in general can be half as long. It only remains to rely on your attentiveness and the hints of travelers from other worlds.\r\n\r\nBut I do not have to puzzle over the question of \"where to go and what to do\". Goals are perfectly read, and the road is just one. True, for the time being. At first the game helps to avoid unpleasant encounters with horrors, which the hero still has the teeth, but as soon as he accumulates enough souls, the world will release his cold hand, and after that the paths and goals will have to be found independently. Careless travelers run the risk of getting stuck and getting lost ...\r\n\r\n... but you did know what you subscribed to?\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"artimage_block\"><a><img class=\"artimg\" title=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/3412140be013b120.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<table class=\"mit_table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; width: 318px;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/ec480cfe380f0816.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td><img style=\"border: 1px solid #888888; outline: none; margin: 6px 8px; display: inline-block; width: 318px;\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/e10994b63e93fde4.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td class=\"mit_desc\" colspan=\"2\">►New locations adopted the severe medieval forms from the first Dark Souls, and the refined \"Victorian\" curves of the Bloodborne. But the main thing is that they still can tell the whole story without words, with their own appearance.</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\nBut the game fully rewards for the time spent. At the most persistent researchers all the fragments of the mosaic will form a single picture, the sequence of events will be restored, and the whole series will merge into one big story. But for this you have to cling literally for each thread, study every bit of information and read a lot between the lines. The series has remained true to the principles of plot submission, so nobody will speak to you directly.\r\n<h1>Conquering the North</h1>\r\nBut the lands on which our chosen dead man wanders, the world of Dark Souls 3 is not limited. Around there are many kingdoms and principalities, and most of them we have heard more than once. The call of the ashes spreads everywhere. The devastated pilgrims from London, the noble knights of Mirra and Astor, the wise wizards of Vinheim - all draw together to the castle of Lotrik, trying to find the missing lords. Or pursuing your own goals.\r\n\r\nMany of them will meet you on the road and become reliable allies or bitter enemies. Sometimes it depends on your actions, and sometimes - just a blind fate, but, anyway, random acquaintances here are not trusted to be trusted. And let the story lines connected with the opposing heroes, in comparison with the first part, be diminished, each of them takes for the soul no worse than the journey of the good-natured Knight Soler, and the denouement of some stories may seem cruel even by the standards of the Dark Souls series.\r\n<div class=\"artimage_block\"><a><img class=\"artimg\" title=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/3b33a111f807ecf5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<table class=\"mit_table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/7995c10d6513ab79.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://cdn.igromania.ru/mnt/articles/8/7/4/2/7/3/27677/html/img/dc99a57a1288cec5.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></td>\r\n</